EASEL ON


              RP Term Rate Balance Table - Help

     Used to determine a rate incentive for an account based
     on either the combined balance of a relationship or an
     individual balance from the specific account and the
     time period (Term) of the account. This panel
     is accessed when using a rate option on the MICM 7103
     panel that requires a term table to be entered.






